  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is buffet style with fresh pastries, yoghurt, bread, cheeses, cold cuts, cereal and fruit.</p>
<p>Half-Board is taken in the hotel's own restaurant which is a rustic wood-panelled dining room. For dinner you'll get three courses and a salad buffet on the side. The hotel's restaurant is known for it's food, they have a great selection of local Valtellina recipes and fresh fish from the lake. All the food is made using fresh ingredients and local produce. What we like to do is try a different wine each night to go with our meal- they have a great wine selection.</p>
<p>You have to go to the gala dinner which takes place once a week, where you can try some delicious local dishes.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
