  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> are about 18m² and sleep up to three people. The extra bed is a single sofa bed. The rooms are decorated in a cosy alpine style. They have a shower, TV, safe and hairdryer. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are more spacious at about 20m² and sleep up to two people.  They have a balcony, mini-bar, tea and coffee making facilities and bath with a showerhead.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are about 32-34m² and sleep up to four people. They are made up of a double bedroom and a separate lounge area with a double sofa bed. They have a jacuzzi bath with a showerhead. </p>
<p><strong>Single rooms</strong> are also available.</p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
